noteType=7
noteToRead="Claire,

This is how you treat me?
I bring you into this
world and you treat me
like this?
You think these grades
are acceptable here?
Get over here now, Claire!

Oh, your daddy's home
now, everything will be
sweetness and light."

if global.gateHProg>=17 {instance_destroy()}
else if global.gateHProg<=15 {y+=256}
